Types
TypeDefinition

Array of arrays in format: [[key1,value1],[key2,value2]...]

Description

Similar to the array used when making hashmaps but, contains extra features such as the preset keys "#str" and "#create" for use in HashmapObjects

See also:

  • HashmapObjects

  • <main.XPS_fnc_buildTypeDefinition>

  • <main.XPS_fnc_preprocessTypeDefinition>

Interface

Array of arrays in format: [[key1,type1],[key2,type2]...] where 'type' is the STRING of the native type (e.g. "STRING","HASHMAP","CODE",etc...)  of the command typeName

Description

Used to ensure a TypeDefinition contains keys that have values of a specific type

See also:

  • TypeDefinition

  • <main.XPS_fnc_checkInterface>
